    {
      "id": "f109cd41-08bf-44fa-8c9a-71d2be3bfc70",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "In this work, the authors use an automated system to predict student dropout. First, they start with clustering courses together based on their design and similarity. Secondly, a predictive model of dropout is specifically created for each cluster. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "f109cd41-08bf-44fa-8c9a-71d2be3bfc70",
        "parent": {
